 ## ⚡ Quick Usage
-
 ### Interactive commit workflow
-
 ``` bash
 git-assistant
 ```
-
 ### Include all files automatically
-
 ``` bash
 git-assistant --all-files
 ```
-
 ### Test workflow without committing
-
 ``` bash
 git-assistant --dry-run
 ```
-
 ### Enable debug diagnostics
-
 ``` bash
 git-assistant --debug
 ```
-
