 ## 📂 File Selection
-
 You can select files using:
-
 ```text
     1,2,4
 ```
-
 Ranges:
-
 ```text
     1-4
 ```
-
 Or combinations:
-
 ```text
     1-4,7,9
 ```
-
 Special option:
-
 ```text
     0
 ```
-
 Includes **all selectable files**.
-
